Convert a pgraster to tabular format

Source: R/utility.R
raster_to_pgtibble.Rd

Convert a pgraster to tabular format

Usage

raster_to_pgtibble(r)

Arguments

r

An input raster that must have the same projection, resolution, and extent as PRIO-GRID

Value

tibble

Examples

pg <- prio_blank_grid()
names(pg) <- "test"
raster_to_pgtibble(pg)
